ily in his fine garment, so Allah ordered the earth to seize him. He is sinking into it until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2491\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18139,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/17\/closest-akhirah-just-imams\/","url_meta":{"origin":14871,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Justice: Closest to Allah in Hereafter are just leaders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most beloved of people to Allah on the Day of Resurrection and the nearest to Him will be the just leader. The most hated of people to Allah and the furthest from Him will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32335,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/free-of-kibr-ghulul-dayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":14871,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Debt: Paradise if he dies free of arrogance, theft, debt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever dies innocent of these three, arrogance, embezzlement, and debt, he will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1572 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u062